Right... okay, I saw that in my Haynes manual.  The trouble is, I can't get
my motor to TDC. As I mentioned in my original post, I can't turn the pulley
to TDC.  It will get within 5 degrees of it, and then it seems to bind up.
This is with the plugs in or out.  Doesn't matter if I am going clockwise,
or counter-clockwise to get there either.  That is where I was most stumped.

